title: Buju Banton - The Early Years: 1990 - 1995 (2007) [FLAC]
description:
http://i.imgur.com/YoJyE2e.jpg



A montage of Buju's earliest and some would say best work as a deejay. From his debut on the hard streets of Kingston to just before converting to reastafarianism, this album includes a number of big (and controversial) hits that were never released on albums previously, and is as a must-have for any dancehall reggae fan!
